articles.author: Joe Miller
articles.title: Sam Bankman-Fried fails to dismiss criminal charges related to FTX - Financial Times
articles.description: Former entrepreneur is set to stand trial in October over the dramatic collapse of his crypto exchange
articles.content:
Sam Bankman-Fried must face the full suite of criminal charges brought against him over the multibillion-dollar collapse of his FTX cryptocurrency exchange, a New York court has ruled.
